      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n        \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\" alt\u003d\"\" alt\u003d\"App Icon\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eClinical Trial Analytical App\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003eThis applications enpowers clinical data managers, CRAs, and biostatsiticians to detect data anomalies in clinical trial datasets using machine-leanring based techniquies. It leverages historical and ongoing clinical data to uncover irregularities and deviations from protocol. The app streamlines data quality monitoring and reduces manual review burden.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eClinical trial data\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eTrained anomaly detection model\u003c/li\u003e\r\n       \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eFlagged anomaly data points summary table\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eAnomaly scores and types per variable/subject/visit\u003c/li\u003e\r\n       \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eBenefits\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eEnhances data quality monitoring\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eReduces protocol deviations and rise of submission rejection\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eAccelerates query resolution workflows through early detection\u003c/li\u003e\r